column5: Hello, Just started fishing recently and I love it, do you know any good fishing spots around Scarborough, Markham, Pickering area?
can't help with the locations  but welcome aboard
First newbie on the new site... TJ give him a prize   .
Welcome aboard, I hear lake x has some really good fishing!
Try hitting up the bluffers park in Scarborough. welcome
Not sure about Scarborough or Markham but in Pickering, the harbour can produce some nice pike and carp.  Welcome to the board and good luck!
